---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Markdown Wiki</title>
    <meta name="description" content="基于 Astro 的轻量级文档站点 · 纯静态 · 零运行时" />

    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://rsms.me/" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://rsms.me/inter/inter.css" />

    <style>
      :root {
        --color-bg: #fff; --color-fg: #171717; --color-muted: #737373;
        --color-border: #e5e5e5; --color-accent: #7c3aed;
        --color-accent-light: #f5f3ff;
      }
      *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
      body {
        font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
        background: var(--color-bg); color: var(--color-fg);
        min-height: 100vh; line-height: 1.7;
        -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
      }
      a { color: var(--color-accent); text-decoration: none; }
      a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

      .hero {
        display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center;
        justify-content: center; text-align: center;
        min-height: 72vh; padding: 2rem;
        position: relative;
      }
      .hero::before {
        content: '';
        position: absolute; inset: 0;
        background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 0%, rgba(124,58,237,0.07), transparent 55%);
      }
      .hero > * { position: relative; z-index: 1; }

      h1 {
        font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 7vw, 4rem);
        font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -0.03em; line-height: 1.1;
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, #171717 0%, #525252 50%, #a3a3a3 100%);
        -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        background-clip: text;
      }
      h1 .accent {
        -webkit-text-fill-color: var(--color-accent);
      }

      .tagline { font-size: 1.2rem; color: var(--color-muted); margin-top: 1rem; font-weight: 400; }

      .actions { margin-top: 2.25rem; display: flex; gap: 0.75rem; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; }
      .btn {
        display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.35rem;
        padding: 0.7rem 1.75rem;
        border-radius: 0.75rem; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 500;
        transition: all 0.15s; cursor: pointer;
      }
      .btn:hover { text-decoration: none; }
      .btn-primary { background: #171717; color: #fff; }
      .btn-primary:hover { background: #262626; transform: translateY(-1px); }
      .btn-outline { border: 1px solid var(--color-border); background: #fff; color: #404040; }
      .btn-outline:hover { background: var(--color-accent-light); border-color: #d4c4fc; transform: translateY(-1px); }

      .features {
        max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 1.5rem 4rem;
        display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
        gap: 1.25rem;
      }
      .card {
        padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 0.85rem;
        border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
        transition: box-shadow 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
        background: #fff;
      }
      .card:hover { box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); border-color: #dcdcdc; }
      .card-icon { font-size: 1.75rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; display: block; }
      .card h3 { font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: 650; margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }
      .card p { font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-muted); line-height: 1.6; }

      .footer {
        text-align: center; padding: 2.5rem 2rem; font-size: 0.85rem;
        color: var(--color-muted); border-top: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="hero">
      <h1>Markdown <span class="accent">Wiki</span></h1>
      <p class="tagline">轻量级文档站点 · 纯静态 · Astro 驱动</p>
      <div class="actions">
          <a href="/docs/getting-started" class="btn btn-primary">
            快速开始
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="m9 18 6-6-6-6"/></svg>
          </a>
          <a href="/docs/dev/architecture" class="btn btn-outline">
            开发指南
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M2 3h6a4 4 0 0 1 4 4v14a3 3 0 0 0-3-3H2z"/><path d="M22 3h-6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v14a3 3 0 0 1 3-3h7z"/></svg>
          </a>
          <a href="https://github.com/Mineocean/TestWiki" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="btn btn-outline" style="padding:0.7rem" title="GitHub">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M15 22v-4a4.8 4.8 0 0 0-1-3.5c3 0 6-2 6-5.5.08-1.25-.27-2.48-1-3.5.28-1.15.28-2.35 0-3.5 0 0-1 0-3 1.5-2.64-.5-5.36-.5-8 0C6 2 5 2 5 2c-.3 1.15-.3 2.35 0 3.5A5.403 5.403 0 0 0 4 9c0 3.5 3 5.5 6 5.5-.39.49-.68 1.05-.85 1.65-.17.6-.22 1.23-.15 1.85v4"/>
              <path d="M9 18c-4.51 2-5-2-7-2"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <section class="features">
      <div class="card">
        <span class="card-icon">⚡</span>
        <h3>零 JS 默认</h3>
        <p>Astro 默认输出纯静态 HTML+CSS，仅在需要交互时添加少量 JS，首屏几乎瞬时加载。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <span class="card-icon">🔍</span>
        <h3>智能导航</h3>
        <p>可折叠侧边栏 + 滚动高亮目录，助你快速定位目标内容。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <span class="card-icon">🚀</span>
        <h3>一键部署</h3>
        <p>输出纯静态文件，可直接部署到 Vercel、Netlify、Cloudflare Pages 等平台。</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <footer class="footer">
      <p>Powered by Astro · Deploy anywhere</p>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
